| Component | App State Coupling | Complexity |
|-----------|-------------------|------------|
| **Provider Tracking** | Per-app current provider HashMap | Medium |
| **Failover Logic** | Per-app circuit breakers, routable checks | High |
| **Live Config Sync** | Per-app backup updates, tray menu | High |
